Traffic on the main line flowed steady. Cars on Minnewashta Pkwy had difficulty getting out, but the longest delay noted was at 5:15 PM - cars
waitied 5 minutes to move, but they found a gap so they were all able to go at the same time. In the AM, the average was 1 to 2.5 minutes.
